    <item>
      <title>中国股市、人民币尾盘反弹，因政治局作出承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国家高层领导人承诺放松货币政策并表示将采取措施刺激消费，在香港上市的中国股票在交易的最后一个小时出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/chinese-stocks-yuan-stage-late-rebound-on-politburo-pledges</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放松货币政策立场，承诺提供更多财政支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普下个月上任，北京方面准备应对第二场贸易战，中国高层领导计划明年放松货币政策并扩大财政支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Boliden 斥资高达 15 亿美元收购 Lundin 锌矿和铜矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/lundin-to-sell-mines-in-portugal-sweden-for-up-to-1-52-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Boliden AB 同意以高达 15.2 亿美元的价格从 Lundin Mining Corp. 手中收购葡萄牙和瑞典的锌矿和铜矿，这笔交易将增强其冶炼厂的矿石供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/lundin-to-sell-mines-in-portugal-sweden-for-up-to-1-52-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 06:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡叙利亚政权垮台后果，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价上涨，因市场衡量叙利亚政府倒台的后果，叙利亚政府倒台给中东地区带来冲击，并给长期支持者俄罗斯和伊朗带来打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 23:25:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治风险下中国转变提振股市：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周初，中东、韩国等地的政治动荡以及各大央行的利率决议将成为主要关注对象，而中国货币政策立场的转变为市场带来了一丝喘息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
