      <title>期权巨头 Optiver 押注日本市场即将繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/options-giant-optiver-is-betting-japan-s-market-is-about-to-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Optiver 正在日本扩张其衍生品业务，旨在推动迄今为止几乎不存在的单一股票期权市场的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/options-giant-optiver-is-betting-japan-s-market-is-about-to-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治危机加剧，韩国股市和韩元暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受周末政治动荡影响，韩国股市暴跌，韩元跌至 2009 年以来最低水平，导致投资者准备迎接一段时间的剧烈波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/traders-brace-for-more-volatility-on-korea-s-political-stalemate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行在意大利建立防御体系以对抗意大利联合信贷银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/credit-agricole-moves-to-shield-italian-business-against-unicredit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）对其规模较小的意大利竞争对手发出收购要约后，法国农业信贷银行（Credit Agricole SA）增持 Banco BPM 股份的举措旨在保护其在意大利的商业利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/credit-agricole-moves-to-shield-italian-business-against-unicredit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 10:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
